  "title": "Fuel and Fire Over Varonat",
  "summary": "A New Republic strike force jumps into the Varonat system to destroy an Imperial refueling station guarding a key junction on the Ison Trade Corridor. Colonel Leo Corak coordinates the A-wings and X-wings of Falcon, Rogue, Ghost, and Dagger squadrons to screen the bombers, while hotshots like Marl 'Gambit' Jace, Crash 'Speed' Thomas, and Lance 'Wildman' Corbet tangle with the Imperial Avengers led by Wing Commander Liza Molokai and the veteran pilot Grey. Commander Rasi Cen brings the cruiser Rapier forward to absorb the Star Destroyer's fire and cover the bombing run, navigated by Lieutenant Siren Delamont. The bombers finally rupture a fuel conduit, igniting the station in a chain of explosions, and the Republic forces withdraw cleanly from the system.",
